{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setTargetCoordinate:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"targetCoordinate"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"animated:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"BOOL","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"animated"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The target coordinate to fit within the viewport."}]}],"name":"targetCoordinate"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"type":"text","text":", the map animates to fit the target within the map"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view. If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"type":"text","text":", the map fits the target instantaneously."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"animated"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"By default, the target coordinate is set to an invalid coordinate, indicating"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"that there is no target. In course tracking mode, the target forms one of two"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"foci in the viewport, the other being the user location annotation. Typically,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the target is set to a destination or waypoint in a real-time navigation scene."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"As the user annotation moves toward the target, the map automatically zooms in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to fit both foci optimally within the viewport."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This method has no effect if the "},{"code":"userTrackingMode","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" property is set to a value"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"other than "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserTrackingMode\/MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To specify a completion handler to execute after the animation finishes, use"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-setTargetCoordinate:animated:completionHandler:"},{"type":"text","text":" method."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/setTargetCoordinate:animated:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"metadata":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:","platforms":[{"unavailable":false,"beta":false,"deprecated":true}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L775","fileName":"MLNMapView.h"},"symbolKind":"method","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(im)setTargetCoordinate:animated:"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/settargetcoordinate:animated:"]}],"abstract":[{"text":"Deprecated. Sets the geog